org.jgentleframework.configure.objectmeta
Interface ObjectBindingConstant

public interface ObjectBindingConstant

Represents an ObjectBindingConstant which is responsible for mapping management and injected data controller. An ObjectBindingConstant holds all configuration information of one bean appropriate to one uniqueID. The configuration data is held in ObjectBindingConstant shall be used in order to instantiate bean. The configuration includes information of ObjectBindingConstant ... and all specified wiring bean information bound to bean.

lazyInit

ObjectBindingConstant lazyInit(boolean lazy_init)
Set the lazy-init value to current ObjectBindingConstant. The lazy-init attribute indicates the bean instantiation by container. As default, the container will automatic insntantiate bean at time bean is invoked. If the lazy-init value is set be false, container implementations will eagerly pre-instantiate bean at startup.

Note: the default value of lazy-init is true and the lazy-init attribute is not supported to prototype-scoped bean.

Parameters:
lazy_init - the specified lazy-init value.
Returns:
ObjectBindingConstant
